investigation into the cause of the accident 
police cordoned off the area but from an adjacent platform it 
was possible to see the twisted wreckage and the emergency medical 
center set up to treat the injured 
authorities said the cause of the accident had not been 
determined officials of the stateowned railroad societe nationale 
chemin de fer said the moving train might have entered the 
underground track too fast and been unable to stop 
