disneys touchstone pictures produced mostly by paramount alumni 
exhibit the same tendencies the films have the same kind of 
homogeneity of the warner bros movies of the 1930s but without an 
equal vitality 
the formula has obviously worked wonders at the boxoffice 
beverly hills cop top gun but the sameness of product 
may be responsible for paramounts precipitous drop before 
crocodile dundee ii in its share of the nations theater 
business 
