raising a key money market intervention rate of its own 
major banks such as barclays bank plc midland bank plc 
national westminster bank plc and lloyds bank plc announced they 
were increasing their rate the banks also increased the base 
lending rate half a percentage point on june 2 june 6 and june 22 
corporate borrowers can obtain loans at a percentage point above 
the base rate 
